  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/cbdf81a6b07595c3acf3f5563afe4a5b.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/cbdf81a6b07595c3acf3f5563afe4a5b.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/cbdf81a6b07595c3acf3f5563afe4a5b.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>You can use magic by attaching a magic piece containing magic to a magic book.</strong></i><br><br><br>Attaching a Magic piece of the same magic will enhance that magic.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/8edb52b3707a84da7316407aaa17dde4.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/8edb52b3707a84da7316407aaa17dde4.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/8edb52b3707a84da7316407aaa17dde4.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you don't like the shape of the magic piece, you can reshape it at the magic altar.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/354ed939ff50d32135761d5684453a06.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/354ed939ff50d32135761d5684453a06.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/354ed939ff50d32135761d5684453a06.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>When you complete a magic sigil with magic pieces, the effect of the magic paper is triggerd.</strong></i><br><br><br>You can exchange magic sigils.<br><br><br>You can change the order of your skills by dragging and dropping the icons in the skill slots.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/d6c60339dd8fba63e05bfac32ee49f2f.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/d6c60339dd8fba63e05bfac32ee49f2f.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/d6c60339dd8fba63e05bfac32ee49f2f.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/b0c83de8a59d7f38851b418a73892e29.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/b0c83de8a59d7f38851b418a73892e29.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/b0c83de8a59d7f38851b418a73892e29.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/65b5ddbf57d05ddca429668295c83a1e.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/65b5ddbf57d05ddca429668295c83a1e.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/65b5ddbf57d05ddca429668295c83a1e.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>You can explore dungeons with unique monsters and bosses.</strong></i><br><br><br>You can teleport to the room you passed by by clicking the icon on the minimap.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/814f6c3be66176d8c6cfc2dec1390d1b.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/814f6c3be66176d8c6cfc2dec1390d1b.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/814f6c3be66176d8c6cfc2dec1390d1b.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In the dungeon, you can trade with goblins who sell potions and magic pieces.<br><br><br>Collect gems from bosses and enter the Devil Castle to defeat the Dark Lord!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/a1a07f20040e8f2c251d88df23dfa286.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/a1a07f20040e8f2c251d88df23dfa286.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/a1a07f20040e8f2c251d88df23dfa286.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/cbdf81a6b07595c3acf3f5563afe4a5b.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/cbdf81a6b07595c3acf3f5563afe4a5b.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/cbdf81a6b07595c3acf3f5563afe4a5b.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>You can use magic by attaching a magic piece containing magic to a magic book.</strong></i><br><br><br>Attaching a Magic piece of the same magic will enhance that magic.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/8edb52b3707a84da7316407aaa17dde4.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/8edb52b3707a84da7316407aaa17dde4.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/8edb52b3707a84da7316407aaa17dde4.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you don't like the shape of the magic piece, you can reshape it at the magic altar.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/354ed939ff50d32135761d5684453a06.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/354ed939ff50d32135761d5684453a06.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><sourc